=== 其它爭議 ===

* 由於在他們的一些襯衫上印上了標語，Forever 21的服裝在媒體上受到了批評。 《每日郵報》“赫芬頓郵報”和其他人堅持稱，該公司“正在推動一項基督教議程”，因為它出售以“聖潔”，“愛，和平，信仰，希望，耶穌”和“感謝上帝”等詞語的上衣。<ref>Dumas, Daisy. "Fashion Chain Forever 21 Accused of Pushing Religious Agenda with Christian-themed T-shirts." Mail Online. The Daily Mail, 11 Aug. 2011. Web. 23 Apr. 2014. <http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-2025046/Fashion-chain-Forever-21-accused-pushing-religious-agenda-Christian-themed-T-shirts.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-2025046/Fashion-chain-Forever-21-accused-pushing-religious-agenda-Christian-themed-T-shirts.html |date=20170615002229 }}>.</ref>同樣，Forever 21在媒體上受到關注，因為他們在他們標誌性的黃色袋子底部印刷了聖經經文“約翰3:16”<ref name="Evangelism">Kolben, Deborah. "Evangelism in Fashion." The New York Sun. N.p., 18 Aug. 2006. Web. 29 Apr. 2014. <http://www.nysun.com/new-york/evangelism-in-fashion/38174/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.nysun.com/new-york/evangelism-in-fashion/38174/ |date=20180803104017 }}>.</ref>該公司堅持認為它不受其是重生基督徒的創始人的宗教影響。 此外，美國廣播公司新聞，Reddit的眾多用戶以及其他人在2011年譴責Forever 21的“Allergic to Algebra(對代數過敏)”襯衫。<ref name="AllergicAlgebraABC">Ng, Christina. "Forever 21′s ‘Allergic to Algebra’ Shirt Draws Criticism." ABC News. ABC News Network, 12 Sept. 2011. Web. 25 Apr. 2014. <http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/headlines/2011/09/forever-21s-allergic-to-algebra-shirt-draws-criticism/ {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/headlines/2011/09/forever-21s-allergic-to-algebra-shirt-draws-criticism/ |date=20181204130947 }}>.</ref>他們宣稱該襯衫具有反教育和性別歧視的主題，但是赫利頓郵報的作家艾莉·克魯普尼克質疑這一點。<ref name="AlgebraHuffington">Krupnick, Ellie. "'Allergic To Algebra' Tee From Forever 21 Under Fire." The Huffington Post. TheHuffingtonPost.com, 12 Sept. 2011. Web. 28 Apr. 2014. <http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/09/12/allergic-to-algebra-forever-21-shirt_n_959063.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/09/12/allergic-to-algebra-forever-21-shirt_n_959063.html |date=20161018211100 }}>.</ref>Krupnick表示，該上衣是在評論數學，而不是性別歧視的評論，並宣布她會穿這件襯衫。
* 2010年4月，作家和Forever 21客戶Rachel Kane創建了一個域名為WTForever21.com的博客。<ref name="Blog">Little, Lyneka.  [//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ABC_News ABC News]. 8 June 2011.  [http://abcnews.go.com/Business/forever-21-threatens-blogger-lawsuit-wtforever21-site/story?id=13784592 Forever 21 Threatens Blogger With Lawsuit for WTForever21 Site] {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Business/forever-21-threatens-blogger-lawsuit-wtforever21-site/story?id=13784592 |date=20180803104519 }}</ref>凱恩張貼了一些Forever 21 產品的照片，並表達了她對服裝的看法。 在Jezebel博客上展示後，該博客的受歡迎程度有所上升，2011年6月，該零售商要求該博主將該網站關閉，否則她可能會面臨訴訟。
